# 📈 Bernie's Stock-Trader App
### Built by Bernard Langan | Always Moving Forward 💪

---

## Overview
A personal stock portfolio tracker and options trading assistant 
built from scratch in Python. Tracks live stock prices, calculates 
gain/loss, screens for covered call opportunities, and monitors 
dividend income.

---

## Features

| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `portfolio.py` | Master holdings data — stocks, shares, buy prices, dividends |
| `tracker.py` | Live portfolio tracker with real time prices and gain/loss |
| `screener.py` | Covered call screener — identifies eligible positions |
| `dividends.py` | Dividend income tracker vs monthly goal |
| `trades.py` | Complete trade history log |
| `alerts.py` | Price alert system — flags big gainers and positions to watch |

